      "body" : "Answering my own question, it apears the spring UriTemplate doesn&#39;t support RFC6570, use the damnhandy implementation: <a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/14153036/how-to-send-array-with-spring-resttemplate\" title=\"how to send array with spring resttemplate\">stackoverflow.com/questions/14153036/&hellip;</a>"
