    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Arrays in <code>@RequestParam</code> are used for binding several parameters of the same name:</p>\n\n<pre><code>myparam=myValue1&amp;myparam=myValue2&amp;myparam=myValue3\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>If you need to bind <code>@ModelAttribute</code>-style indexed parameters, I guess you need <code>@ModelAttribute</code> anyway.</p>\n"
