    "body" : "<p>Or you could just do it that way:</p>\n\n<pre><code>public String controllerMethod(@RequestParam(value=\"myParam[]\") String[] myParams){\n    ....\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>That works for example for forms like this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"myParam[]\" value=\"myVal1\" /&gt;\n&lt;input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"myParam[]\" value=\"myVal2\" /&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>This is the simplest solution :)</p>\n"
