    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Change hidden field value with checkbox toggle like below...</p>\n\n<p><strong>HTML:</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;input type='hidden' value='Unchecked' id=\"deleteAll\" name='anyName'&gt;\n&lt;input type=\"checkbox\"  onclick=\"toggle(this)\"/&gt; Delete All\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>Script:</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>function toggle(obj) {`var $input = $(obj);\n    if ($input.prop('checked')) {\n\n    $('#deleteAll').attr( 'value','Checked');\n\n    } else {\n\n    $('#deleteAll').attr( 'value','Unchecked');\n\n    }\n\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
